### Tweet classifier for climate change
## Resources;

* Twitter data relating to climate change collected between 2015 and 2017

## objectives

    * To use Natural language processing and machine learning models to correctly classify a tweet

    * To help marketing teams to plan marketing strategies and run successfull add campaigns

    * To help marketing teams to correctly make their stance on climate change get well known to clients

    * To help companies build good customer relations with clients and have a returning clients
